                </mxCell>
                <mxCell id="ez4ky4WJp2ajRVcOHQkX-33" value="The schema of the modeling engine itself. (e.g., a JSON schema that dictates the structure of a valid save file for your engine)" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;align=left;spacingLeft=10;" parent="ez4ky4WJp2ajRVcOHQkX-26" vertex="1">
