                <mxCell id="ez4ky4WJp2ajRVcOHQkX-35" value="&lt;div&gt;(entity schema) The schema defined by the specific implementation model (e.g., the schema defining that a &quot;Customer&quot; requires a &quot;String Name&quot;).&lt;/div&gt;" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;align=left;spacingLeft=10;" parent="ez4ky4WJp2ajRVcOHQkX-26" vertex="1">
